#              server framework github.com/99designs/gqlgen.
# ============================================================================
#
# UPSTREAM
#   Repository : https://github.com/empiricaly/empirica
#   Maintainer : Empirica Inc. (the open-source spin-out of the
#                Empirica research-software project at the MIT
#                Center for Constructive Communication, now
